title: SwifTEA: The Joker And The Queen (feat. Taylor Swift)
description:
Ed Sheeran reunited with our Queen once again! The music video picks up right where another left off.. And yes, there are Easter eggs and we (hopefully!) uncover them all!
What do you think of this remix? What did we miss? What would you like to hear from us? Let us know!
